reviewText:
mazing, astonishing, flabbergasting, formidable, exciting, moving, touching!!!
This is not another documentary film, it will be engraved in your head for long long time.

Very interesting to watch those old people who had a lot in their life come back to their history as children at Marc Aurel street.
This is story of the brave people, the pioneers of Israel and their confrontation with the past. This is really inspiring movie.
